# Design System

## Brand Color Tokens (`lib/constants/branding.ts`)

```ts
BRAND.PRIMARY       = "#173f35"   // dark forest green — buttons, active nav, headings
BRAND.PRIMARY_DARK  = "#10231f"   // page headings, strong text
BRAND.PRIMARY_LIGHT = "#245d4e"   // hover state for primary buttons
BRAND.ACCENT        = "#c59b4a"   // gold — secondary CTAs, highlights, badges
BRAND.ACCENT_DARK   = "#b5893a"   // hover state for accent buttons
BRAND.BG            = "#f7f4ef"   // page background — warm off-white
BRAND.BG_WARM       = "#efe3cf"   // card hover backgrounds, callout blocks
BRAND.BORDER        = "#e5ded3"   // all borders and dividers
BRAND.TEXT_MUTED    = "#65736f"   // secondary text, descriptions
BRAND.TEXT_FAINT    = "#8a958f"   // placeholder, metadata, disabled
```

## Component Recipes

### Cards
```tsx
<div className="bg-white border border-[#e5ded3] rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5">
```

### Primary Button
```tsx
<button className="bg-[#173f35] text-white hover:bg-[#245d4e] px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-sm transition-colors shadow-md">
```

### Accent Button
```tsx
<button className="bg-[#c59b4a] text-white hover:bg-[#b5893a] px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-sm transition-colors">
```

### Ghost / Border Button
```tsx
<button className="border border-[#e5ded3] text-[#65736f] hover:bg-[#f7f4ef] hover:text-[#173f35] px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm transition-colors">
```

### Input
```tsx
<input className="w-full border border-[#e5ded3] rounded-xl px-3 py-2.5 text-sm text-[#10231f] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#173f35] placeholder:text-[#8a958f]">
```

### Page Title
```tsx
<h1 className="text-2xl font-bold text-[#10231f]">
<p className="text-[#65736f] text-sm mt-1">
```

### Loading Skeleton
```tsx
<div className="h-24 bg-[#f7f4ef] rounded-2xl animate-pulse">
```

## Rules

- ❌ Never use default Tailwind colors (`blue-500`, `green-600`, `gray-400`) for Zafora UI
- ❌ No `dark:` variants — project has no dark mode
- ✅ Always use `transition-colors` on interactive elements
- ✅ Page background is always `bg-[#f7f4ef]` (admin layout sets this)
- ✅ Admin content area: `space-y-6 max-w-5xl` for wide tables, `max-w-2xl` for forms
